properties.name: Description
properties.value:
Tessera Perspective is a 50 x 50 cm cut & loop pile carpet tile collection that consists of 8 neutral tones complemented by 6 rich, decadent accent colours. Each colour tone combines two yarn colours, creating a modern, softly striated design.

Forbo’s carpet tiles are designed and manufactured with various pile constructions to give specific aesthetic and performance benefits. Cut and loop pile tiles feature a clever hybrid construction that offers all the robustness of a conventional loop pile product but with the superior aesthetics and more luxurious feel of a cut pile carpet tile. 

Benefits: • 100% Universal solution-dyed Nylon 66 and Nylon 6, for class 33 durability and colour fastness • 670 gsm pile weight ensures underfoot comfort and durability • monolithic installation giving the appearance of a broadloom installation • 65% recycled content by weight • high acoustic value of 25 dB for minimal noise transmission • meets Ska criteria for M12 soft floor coverings • easy to combine with Allura Flex luxury vinyl tiles using the same adhesive and without the need for transition strips, additional profiles or inconvenient build-up of the sub-floor
